items.title: Walmart owned PhonePe files for mega IPO of around Rs 12,000 crore via confidential route
items.description: The proposed IPO is a pure OFS or offer for sale with participation from Walmart and investors Tiger Global and Microsoft

items.title: Meta rolls out real-time translation feature on WhatsApp
items.description: The translations will initially be available in six languages on Android devices and 19 languages on iPhones, with more languages to follow

items.title: Tata Capital targets $16.5 bn valuation for its $1.85-bn IPO; early October launch on cards
items.description: Insurance behemoth LIC is likely to participate as an investor in the mega issue, the biggest so far this year

items.title: Amul, Real Juice, Maggi: Here's how much your favourite food brands cost after GST cuts
items.description: The latest version of GST, introduced first in 2017, curtails the number of slabs to just two – 5 percent and 18 percent
